											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="[PN] Show players’ party arriving at ladder (this should be set up in a way that can work for solo player). Other party members ascend the ladder first. Player runs from the corner over to the ladder and ascends, , 1. Show Obelia Toobin running to and climbing up ladder. (Can be absent if not rescued), 2. Show Player 2 encourage trailing player, and goes up the ladder. (Can be absent if solo party)., 3. Show Player 1 arrive late and make up the rear following party up the ladder. (Will always play), , Player ascends the ladder, party cheers them on (this should be set up in a way that can work for solo player e.g. no interaction). PLYR reaction to a door exploding with water pressure below/behind them. Player reaches the top, quickly turns around and shuts airlock door." />
